code: @Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     super.writeTo(out).     if (out.getVersion().before(Version.V_6_6_0)) {         User.writeTo(authentication.getUser(), out).     } else {         authentication.writeTo(out).     } }

@Override public void readFrom(StreamInput in) throws IOException {     super.readFrom(in).     if (in.getVersion().before(Version.V_6_6_0)) {         final User user = User.readFrom(in).         final Authentication.RealmRef unknownRealm = new Authentication.RealmRef("__unknown", "__unknown", "__unknown").         authentication = new Authentication(user, unknownRealm, unknownRealm).     } else {         authentication = new Authentication(in).     } }
